&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Position&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div&gt;We are seeking a highly motivated and data-driven Product Manager to lead the strategy and execution for our Conversation Intelligence product suite. This role involves defining roadmap for a product that leverages AI and machine learning to provide deep, actionable insights from customer conversations, including AI-generated call transcripts, summaries, and sentiment analysis. The goal is to empower small businesses and agencies to better understand their customers, identify pain points, recognize opportunities, and drive business growth.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
